OL,7,FVisa rules will be relaxed to allow
OL,8,Fmore foreign construction workers to
OL,9,Fcome to the UK in a bid to tackle
OL,10,Flabour shortages in certain industries.
OL,12,FThe Government is expected to relax
OL,13,Frules for roofers, plumbers,
OL,14,Fbricklayers, carpenters and plasterers
OL,15,Fto plug gaps in the construction labour
OL,16,Fforce and boost economic growth.
OL,18,FBut there will not be similarly
OL,19,Floosened rules for hospitality staff,
OL,20,Fdespite repeated calls from those in
OL,21,Fthe sector to do so, i understands.
OL,3,CVisa rules to be relaxed for
OL,4,Cconstruction workers in a bid to plug
OL,5,Cpost-Brexit labour shortages
